   * the 'paths.h' header (not required, actually, but a good thing to
     have)
   * the 'fork()' function
   * the 'execvp()' function
   * the 'dup2()' function
   * the 'close()' function
   * the 'pipe()' function
   * the 'kill()' function
   * the 'waitpid()' or 'wait()' function
   * the 'sleep()' function (not required, actually, but a good thing to
     have)
   * the 'long long' data type support in the compiler
